lines: 1. Puothe chiek e pinje duto,Nitie cham mathoth maber;E pewe gi holni dutoCham orito jokeyo.
Ruodhwa, wan wayuakni koro,Ni mond` ior jokeyo;Ni mondo gichok cham duto,Nyaka keyo rum chutho.
2. Orgi ka chieng` wuok gokinyi,Orgi kata godiechieng`,Kata saa ma wang` chieng` podho,pod onego gitim tich.
3. Un jokeyo ma Ruoth oro,Chokuru cham mosechiek;To ka tich me piny ka rumoUnubed gi mor maduong`.
